text: A tip for anyone encountering a launch aborted message. One solution that I found worked was to duplicate my virtual machine in the main menu. You can do this by right clicking the machine in question and clicking clone. In my case, while the original was unable to run, the clone ran successfully and kept all previous modifications from the original including the full screen function from step 7 of Lab01.
